<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Link Expired — Security Notice</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Inter:400,600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #18181b;
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .card {
            background: #232329;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(37,99,235,0.07);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 2.2rem 2rem 2rem 2rem;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 94vw;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            animation: fadeIn 0.7s;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px);}
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);}
        }
        .big-emoji {
            font-size: 2.8em;
            margin-bottom: 0.7em;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #f59e42;
            margin-bottom: 0.3em;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .desc {
            color: #fafafa;
            font-size: 1.08rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.2em;
        }
        .caught {
            background: #fbbf24;
            color: #232329;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 0.45em 1em;
            margin-bottom: 1.1em;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(251,191,36,0.07);
        }
        .notice {
            color: #fbbf24;
            font-size: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 0.7em;
            margin-top: -0.4em;
        }
        .footer {
            color: #a1a1aa;
            font-size: 0.99em;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 1.1em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="big-emoji">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield"></i>
        </div>
        <h2>Link Expired</h2>
        <div class="desc">
            This secure link was valid for <strong>one-time use only</strong>.<br>
            <div class="caught">ACCESS DENIED</div>
            The file is no longer available. Further attempts to access this link are not permitted.
        </div>
        <div class="notice">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
            For security reasons, your IP address has been tracked.<br>
            All activities are logged and monitored.
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-lock"></i> Secure One-Time Sharing — AWS S3
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 